.com/articles/archives/1980/feb/21/eye-of-the-storm/ Eye of the Storm]\", in &apos;&apos;[[The New York Review of Books]]&apos;&apos;, Volume XXVII, Number 2, 21 February 1980, pp.&amp;nbsp;36–43; reprinted as [http://www.syberberg.de/Syberberg4_2010/Susan-Sontag-Syberbergs-Hitler-engl.html \"Syberberg&apos;s Hitler\"] in &apos;&apos;[[Under the Sign of Saturn]]&apos;&apos;. New York: [[Farrar, Straus and Giroux]], 1980, ",{"template":{"target":{"wt":"ISBN","href":"./Template:ISBN"},"params":{"1":{"wt":"978-0-86316-052-3"}},"i":68}},", 137–165.\n* Spencer, Stewart (2000), &apos;&apos;Wagner Remembered&apos;&apos;, London: Faber and Faber. ",{"template":{"target":{"wt":"ISBN","href":"./Template:ISBN"},"params":{"1":{"wt":"978-0-571-19653-1"}},"i":69}},".\n* Spencer, Stewart (2008), \"The &apos;Romantic operas&apos; and the turn to myth\", in Grey (2008), 67–73.\n* Spotts, Frederic (1994), &apos;&apos;Bayreuth: A History of the Wagner Festival&apos;&apos;, New Haven and London: Yale University Press. ",{"template":{"target":{"wt":"ISBN","href":"./Template:ISBN"},"params":{"1":{"wt":"978-0-300-06665-4"}},"i":70}},".\n* Stanley, Glenn (2008), \"Parsifal: redemption and &apos;&apos;Kunstreligion&apos;&apos;\", in Grey (2008), 151–75.\n* Tanner, M. (1995), &apos;&apos;Wagner&apos;&apos;, Princeton: Princeton University Press. ",{"template":{"target":{"wt":"ISBN","href":"./Template:ISBN"},"params":{"1":{"wt":"978-0-691-10290-0"}},"i":71}},".\n* [[Richard Taruskin|Taruskin, Richard]] (2009), &apos;&apos;Music in the Early Twentieth Century&apos;&apos;, Oxford: Oxford University Press. ",{"template":{"target":{"wt":"ISBN","href":"./Template:ISBN"},"params":{"1":{"wt":"978-0-19-538484-0"}},"i":72}},".\n* Treadwell, James (2008), \"The Urge to Communicate\", in Grey (2008), 179–91.\n* Vaszonyi, Nicholas (2010), &apos;&apos;Richard Wagner: Self-Promotion and the Making of a Brand&apos;&apos;. Cambridge: Cambridge University Press. ",{"template":{"target":{"wt":"ISBN","href":"./