<section data-mw-section-id="38" id="mwBAk"><h3 id="Operas_2">Operas</h3>
<ul id="mwBAo"><li id="mwBAs"><a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="http://www.wagneropera.net/" id="mwBAw">Richard Wagner Opera</a>, Richard Wagner operas, Wagner interviews, CDs, DVDs, Wagner calendar, Bayreuth Festival</li>
<li id="mwBA0"><a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="http://www.wagneroperas.com/" id="mwBA4">Wagner Operas</a>, site featuring photographs, video, MIDI files, scores, libretti, and commentary</li>
